Name: Cubanoids
About the game: Cubanoids is a mix of action and survival game. Game developed entirely by one person Sit down, turn on the game and relax. Key features: • Single player • Local cooperative for 2 players • Two different game modes - Survival - Hero Defense • Low-poly graphics • 7 characters • Controller support • Two arenas • Creeps, powerups and fun
